Grading Scales
==============

.. data:: DEFAULT_SCALE

    The standard grading scale as an OrderedDict. E.g., 93+ is an A, [90, 93)
    is an A-, etc.

.. data:: ROUNDED_DEFAULT_SCALE

    A rounded version of the default scale in which each threshold is one half point lower.

